window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Join Dale as he continues to grow as a Keeper. With the experiences slowly piling up around him, how will he deal with the changes to come? Is he ready for all that awaits him?</p> <p>His world has stepped out of its earliest stages, moving on to bigger and better things while Dale and his pantheon watch from above.</p> <p>See how his decisions impact the course of history, and watch as he shapes the world with the help of those around him.</p>"; 
